A 5-minute ETHUSDT trading strategy that trades in the direction of the higher timeframe:30-minute EMA trend filter: Only long when uptrend, only short when downtrendEntry trigger: Price retests the Bollinger Band midline + 2 consecutive bullish/bearish candlesDynamic trailing stop: ATR-based trailing exit to lock in profits✅ Supports long-only, short-only, or full long/short mode
💡 Fully compatible with Gate.io, Bybit, and other exchanges supporting trailing stops
